*Igre* su moj najdraži hobiji. (Games are my favorite hobbies.)

*Igrao* sam svoje omiljene igrice ceo dan. (I played my favorite video games all day.)

U školi su nam često pravili *igre* da bi se naučilo nešto novo. (In school they often made games to learn something new.)

Moji prijatelji i ja smo često odigrali neku od naših omiljenih *igara*. (My friends and I often played one of our favorite games.)

Naši roditelji su nam dozvoljavali da se igramo koliko god želimo, ali uvek smo morali da se *igramo* po pravilima. (Our parents allowed us to play as much as we wanted, but we always had to play by the rules.)